Thus, \(w_1 = 2(-1) = -2\) and \(w_2 = 5(-1) = -5\). Therefore, the vector \(\begin{pmatrix} w_1 \\ w_2 \end{pmatrix}\) is \(\begin{pmatrix} -2 \\ -5 \end{pmatrix}\).

