\[
b_2 = 2018^{\frac{1}{2017}} \cdot 7^{1 - \frac{1}{2017}}
\]
\[
b_2 = 2018^{\frac{1}{2017}} \cdot 7^{\frac{2016}{2017}}
\]

To simplify, we notice that \( 2018 = 2 \times 1009 \), which is not a power of 7. Therefore, we express \( b_2 \) as:
\[
