I0320 16:37:51.427551 127102378575424 reward_manager.py:164] prompts:	Tom's grandmother's age is three times Tom's age plus 10 years. If Tom's grandmother was 30 years old when Tom's father was born, and Tom's father is currently twice as old as Tom, how many years old is Tom now?
