   \]

5. **Year 5:**
   \[
   \text{Balance} = 1402.70 \times (1 + 0.06) = 1402.70 \times 1.06 = 1487.86
   \]

Rounding the final balance to the nearest whole number, the value of the account after five years is approximately \(\boxed{1488}\).
