I0320 17:56:29.371039 127102378575424 reward_manager.py:164] completions:	 To determine the value of \( n \) such that the graphs of \( h(x) = x^3 - 3x^2 + n \) and \( k(x) = x^3 - 3x^2 + 2n \) intersect at exactly two points, we start by setting up the problem:

