\[
88 + 92 + x \geq 90 \cdot 3
\]

\[
180 + x \geq 270
\]

Next, subtract 180 from both sides to solve for \( x \):

\[
x \geq 270 - 180
\]

\[
x \geq 90
\]

Therefore, Emily needs a minimum score of \boxed{90}
\] on her third science exam to maintain an average grade of at least 90%.
