I0320 19:06:48.927084 127102378575424 reward_manager.py:164] completions:	 To solve this problem, we need to find the largest number of cups of flour that can be divided evenly among the three types of bread. This involves finding the maximum number of complete batches of each type of bread that can be prepared without leaving any flour behind.

