The final matrix $A$ is indeed
\[ \boxed{A} = \begin{pmatrix} 0 & -1 & 0 \\ 0 & 0 & -1 \\ 1 & 0 & 0 \end{pmatrix} \]

Thus, the correct answer is $\boxed{A} = \boxed{0}$. And so, the correct answer must be \( \boxed{0} \).

